These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: metal, funk, indie, punk, d&b, house
6 different pets are kept: snake, bird, rat, hamster, goat, lizard
 1. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4
 2. the fan of house is somewhere to the left of the fan of funk##5
 3. the fan of d&b is not the owner of the goat##6
 4. the fan of punk is somewhere to the left of the fan of funk##5
 5. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5
 6. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
 7. the owner of the goat is not the fan of funk##6
 8. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of metal is somewhere between the owner of the lizard and the fan of punk##7
10. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
11. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
12. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
13. the owner of the snake is the fan of metal##1
14. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the fan of d&b##5
15. the fan of house is the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | punk   | metal | indie   | house     | funk    | d&b   |
| Pet           | goat | snake   | lizard | hamster | rat | bird |

