.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: epic, western, zombie, comedy, action, satire
6 different pets are kept: goldfish, frog, goat, ferret, cat, bird
 1. the person watching epic movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching western movies##5
 2. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
 3. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
 4. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
 5. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 6. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
 7. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5
 8. the person watching epic movies is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person watching action movies is not the owner of the cat##6
10. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the owner of the bird and the owner of the ferret##7
11. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the person watching action movies##5
12. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
13. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
14. the owner of the bird is in an even position##4
15. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
16. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
17. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere between the owner of the frog and the person watching action movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |     5      |    6     |
| Movie-Genre   | western | satire | comedy | action     | zombie      | epic |
| Pet           | frog         | goat        | cat   | ferret | goldfish | bird    |

