.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-3::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, milk, coffee, 7up, sprite
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: soccer, snowboarding, weightlifting, golf, cricket, rowing
 1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##5
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not the person drinking coffee##6
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is not the person who's sport is soccer##6
 6. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
10. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking juice##7
11. the person who's sport is rowing is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
13. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##5
14. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rowing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |    5     |       6       |
| Beverage   | 7up        | coffee | sprite    | iced-tea    | milk | juice |
| Sport      | snowboarding | cricket  | rowing | golf | soccer | weightlifting      |

