 8. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 9. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person drinking sprite##7
10. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
11. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
12. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching satire movies##5
13. the person watching family movies is the person drinking sprite##1
14. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5

