.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: woodworking, chess, reading, board-games, sudoku, gardening
The people have 6 different jobs:  freelancer, chef, entrepreneur, teacher, police-officer, analyst
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
 2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the entrepreneur##5
 4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere between the teacher and the chef##7
 5. the analyst is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
 6. the person who's hobby is reading is the police-officer##1
 7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the teacher##5
 8. the police-officer is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##5
 9. the police-officer is somewhere to the left of the entrepreneur##5
10. the chef is somewhere to the right of the analyst##5
11. the analyst is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the teacher##5
13. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is reading##7
14. the chef is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
15. the police-officer is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2      |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6      |
| Hobby   | reading         | board-games | chess | woodworking   | gardening | sudoku  |
| Job     | police-officer | teacher  | entrepreneur  | analyst | chef  | freelancer |

 